name: Music ID Tag Key Chain...Red and White Metal Dog Tag Style..handmade by Jennifer Meyers
Cute and Sassy...Red Metal Heart Earrings..Comes with small decorated storage tin
description:
I am breaking into my stash of ear-wires that I hand darkened with liver of sulfur (sounds wild doesn’t it). This gun metal color wire earrings are a hot fashion statement.

	The hearts are hung on large ear wires and have flattened sides. The ear-wire wires are light and swingy, perfect for wearing anytime…especially out dancing!. 
The heart drops measure 16×16mm and are a bright fire-engine red enamel over metal. They have an almost 80’s look to them. Comes with small decorated storage tin.

	Thank You,
Jennifer
